description: This charming 3 bed, 1.5 bath single family is the city home you have been searching for! 4 Ward Ct offers private parking w/ EV outlet, a spacious backyard, AND expansion potential, all with easy access to the highway, Red Line T & bus, as well as all of the restaurants, shops, & beaches Southie has to offer – w/ NO HOA fees! Located at the end of a quiet private way, this home features a bright kitchen/living area w/ stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a center island, gas fireplace, custom built-ins, & a view of the fenced-in yard through sliding doors. The 2nd level is complete w/ a full bath & 3 generously sized bedrooms, including one w/ a cozy deck ideal for morning coffee.The interior staircase leads to a flat roof, offering potential for a 3rd/4th floor or roof deck. Additional highlights include hardwood floors, central A/C, & a full waterproofed basement for added storage or flex space. This must see hidden gem offers the perfect blend of comfort & convenience!
